1
00:00:07,340 --> 00:00:09,379
I'm Qingniao Group's founder

2
00:00:09,380 --> 00:00:12,220
and chief architect, Shen Gu.

3
00:00:12,580 --> 00:00:16,659
Regarding the recent rumors
about Minghui Group and Qingniao Group,

4
00:00:16,660 --> 00:00:19,899
please allow me to clarify everything

5
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:21,460
as Xu Wanxin's husband.

6
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:30,980
Mr. Shen is actually the founder
of Qingniao Group?

7
00:00:31,460 --> 00:00:32,459
That's a global tech giant

8
00:00:32,460 --> 00:00:35,459
valued at hundreds
of billions of dollars.

9
00:00:35,460 --> 00:00:38,780
Qingniao just broke through
quantum encryption patents.

10
00:00:39,500 --> 00:00:41,179
Their infrastructure supports

11
00:00:41,180 --> 00:00:44,260
23 percent of mobile services worldwide.

12
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:48,780
And the founder of that company
is Shen Gu. I can't believe that.

13
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,780
If that's the case,

14
00:00:50,900 --> 00:00:53,060
it makes sense

15
00:00:53,140 --> 00:00:55,100
why Qingniao stepped in

16
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:56,780
when we were facing the crisis.

17
00:01:05,500 --> 00:01:07,340
We'll call it a day.

18
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:14,319
=Echoes of Gang City=

19
00:01:14,320 --> 00:01:19,699
=Episode 19=
(Confession)

20
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:21,740
I'm Qingniao Group's founder.

21
00:01:21,820 --> 00:01:25,020
I should've wiped him out back then.

22
00:01:26,900 --> 00:01:29,140
When he came to Raymond
to look for funding,

23
00:01:30,260 --> 00:01:32,020
he was a poor student.

24
00:01:34,700 --> 00:01:36,100
I didn't expect him

25
00:01:36,580 --> 00:01:38,900
to be the founder of Qingniao.

26
00:01:48,420 --> 00:01:49,740
Grandfather.

27
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:51,780
Wanxin.

28
00:01:51,860 --> 00:01:53,819
The Qingniao chairman

29
00:01:53,820 --> 00:01:56,180
you met in Shen City was Shen Gu?

30
00:01:56,300 --> 00:01:57,940
Why didn't you tell me?

31
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:00,459
Calm down,

32
00:02:00,460 --> 00:02:01,580
Wanxin.

33
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:05,419
I know you feel hurt right now.

34
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:07,220
Why did he do this?

35
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,900
Is it because
we're in a contract marriage,

36
00:02:10,060 --> 00:02:12,059
and he didn't trust me?

37
00:02:12,060 --> 00:02:13,220
Or

38
00:02:14,020 --> 00:02:15,500
is he like the Shen family,

39
00:02:16,180 --> 00:02:17,980
after our company's research?

40
00:02:19,820 --> 00:02:21,540
I can guarantee you

41
00:02:21,860 --> 00:02:23,299
he didn't tell you

42
00:02:23,300 --> 00:02:26,100
for those reasons.

43
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:32,379
Then why didn't you tell Wanxin

44
00:02:32,380 --> 00:02:34,900
you're the president of Qingniao?

45
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:39,540
At first, I just wanted
to help her through the crisis.

46
00:02:40,100 --> 00:02:42,100
I didn't expect
she would propose marriage.

47
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:44,300
I couldn't turn her down.

48
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:46,779
And after that,

49
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:49,980
I never found the right time
to tell her the truth.

50
00:02:50,580 --> 00:02:53,780
There was never any contract marriage
between Wanxin and me,

51
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:55,780
nor any weighing of pros and cons.

52
00:02:57,260 --> 00:03:00,699
I simply wanted to become her husband.

53
00:03:00,700 --> 00:03:05,100
What if things didn't go your way?

54
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:07,300
What if she never fell for you?

55
00:03:08,380 --> 00:03:09,940
If she doesn't love me,

56
00:03:10,700 --> 00:03:12,540
she can leave anytime.

57
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:14,100
That's her choice.

58
00:03:16,130 --> 00:03:18,689
That's what he told me.

59
00:03:18,690 --> 00:03:20,980
I wouldn't lie to you.

60
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:28,340
He appeared so suddenly.

61
00:03:29,460 --> 00:03:30,700
I thought

62
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:33,100
we fell for each other

63
00:03:33,980 --> 00:03:36,020
after we got married.

64
00:03:38,020 --> 00:03:39,140
Grandfather,

65
00:03:41,300 --> 00:03:43,220
I don't know what to do now.

66
00:03:44,180 --> 00:03:46,779
This is between the two of you.

67
00:03:46,780 --> 00:03:50,100
You have to figure it out together.

68
00:04:22,180 --> 00:04:23,260
I'm sorry.

69
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,700
Please allow me
to introduce myself again.

70
00:04:33,940 --> 00:04:35,420
Let's go home and talk.

71
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,420
Shen Gu,

72
00:05:18,620 --> 00:05:20,940
why did you choose to work with Minghui?

73
00:05:30,180 --> 00:05:31,300
Wanxin,

74
00:05:32,180 --> 00:05:34,100
the cooperation
between Qingniao and Minghui

75
00:05:34,580 --> 00:05:38,300
was planned with me
by your dad before he passed away.

76
00:05:43,380 --> 00:05:45,340
Minghui's biotech

77
00:05:46,060 --> 00:05:47,580
and your AI

78
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:49,859
will take our tech sector

79
00:05:49,860 --> 00:05:51,379
to the next level.

80
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:53,419
I've carefully reviewed

81
00:05:53,420 --> 00:05:55,300
all your proposals.

82
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:57,780
They align perfectly with our vision.

83
00:05:58,980 --> 00:06:00,620
But may I ask,

84
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:03,579
why were you so eager
to look for funding

85
00:06:03,580 --> 00:06:05,380
and cut ties with Junlin?

86
00:06:06,020 --> 00:06:07,579
You've worked together for years,

87
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:09,500
and there was even a marriage alliance.

88
00:06:13,020 --> 00:06:14,500
Junlin Group

89
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:17,779
is indeed a powerful partner.

90
00:06:17,780 --> 00:06:21,300
Shen Tingyuan is ambitious.

91
00:06:21,900 --> 00:06:25,380
But his goal is to expand his business.

92
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:29,500
He has lost sight of the original purpose
of our cooperation.

93
00:06:30,380 --> 00:06:33,300
And more importantly,

94
00:06:33,420 --> 00:06:35,380
through my years of observation,

95
00:06:37,620 --> 00:06:41,020
Shen Hao isn't right for my daughter.

96
00:06:41,380 --> 00:06:45,620
I would never gamble
my daughter's happiness.

97
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,220
Thank you for trusting Qingniao.

98
00:07:05,180 --> 00:07:06,300
Wanxin,

99
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:10,260
your dad has always been protecting you.

100
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:19,780
My dad did it for Minghui and me.

101
00:07:22,780 --> 00:07:23,900
What about you?

102
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,140
What's your reason?

103
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:37,620
You.

104
00:07:39,980 --> 00:07:41,900
All those so-called marriage alliances

105
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:43,900
and cooperations

106
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,020
are just excuses.

107
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:49,180
The only reason I did all this

108
00:07:50,780 --> 00:07:52,420
was to stay by your side.

109
00:08:01,310 --> 00:08:06,099
♪It feels like our souls are in sync♪

110
00:08:06,100 --> 00:08:07,060
Wanxin,

111
00:08:09,820 --> 00:08:10,780
I love you.

112
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:13,140
I just hope

113
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:16,420
you won't push me away.

114
00:08:21,010 --> 00:08:26,960
♪As the stars flow,
fate holds this moment still♪

115
00:08:27,300 --> 00:08:33,829
♪At last, your late reply arrives♪

116
00:08:33,830 --> 00:08:40,570
♪At last, I hear your answer clearly♪

117
00:08:40,810 --> 00:08:46,929
♪When you turn around,
I've always been behind you♪

118
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:52,180
♪As long as you're here, I have it all♪

119
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:56,240
♪The whole universe♪

120
00:09:05,460 --> 00:09:08,300
Looks like my news
is more interesting than I am.

121
00:09:10,380 --> 00:09:13,219
You're a big name
in both finance and the media now.

122
00:09:13,220 --> 00:09:14,900
I had no choice but to notice you.

123
00:09:19,620 --> 00:09:21,139
If you want to know something,

124
00:09:21,140 --> 00:09:22,860
just ask me.

125
00:09:27,620 --> 00:09:29,060
They'll be here soon.

126
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:51,819
Where's he going?

127
00:09:51,820 --> 00:09:52,980
To get the wine.

128
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,860
This is for you.

129
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,100
Open it.

130
00:10:19,620 --> 00:10:21,480
Dragon and phoenix
bring auspicious blessings.

131
00:10:22,100 --> 00:10:24,180
A small gift from Madam Song and me.

132
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:39,020
Shen Gu,

133
00:10:40,420 --> 00:10:41,620
take good care of her.

134
00:10:44,700 --> 00:10:45,900
Stop it.

135
00:10:57,980 --> 00:10:58,940
Hello?

136
00:10:59,100 --> 00:11:00,739
Can someone help me?

137
00:11:00,740 --> 00:11:01,580
Coming.

138
00:11:04,300 --> 00:11:05,500
Let's go.

139
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:13,140
Shen Gu's identity is confirmed.

140
00:11:13,420 --> 00:11:16,380
Mr. Lei Meng, what's your plan?

141
00:11:18,180 --> 00:11:20,980
End all pressure on Minghui.

142
00:11:21,700 --> 00:11:24,179
I'll unite Qingniao's competitors

143
00:11:24,180 --> 00:11:25,500
into an alliance

144
00:11:26,220 --> 00:11:28,100
and destroy their core business.

145
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,620
That way,

146
00:11:29,820 --> 00:11:32,020
Raymond Group takes full control

147
00:11:32,100 --> 00:11:33,980
of the industry.

148
00:11:38,140 --> 00:11:39,500
Good.

149
00:11:42,220 --> 00:11:46,900
I'll be relying on your guidance
and support in the future, Mr. Lei Meng.

150
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:55,460
Wait for my good news.

151
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:14,940
Lei Meng is gone. What do we do now?

152
00:12:18,916 --> 00:12:20,020
Lei Meng

153
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:23,020
wants Qingniao dead
even more than we do.

154
00:12:24,980 --> 00:12:26,580
Cheers.

155
00:12:33,980 --> 00:12:36,380
I don't want to sound rude or anything.

156
00:12:36,780 --> 00:12:39,940
We've revealed your identity, Mr. Gu.

157
00:12:40,020 --> 00:12:43,579
But the negative publicity
around Ms. Wanxin and you

158
00:12:43,580 --> 00:12:45,019
hasn't improved.

159
00:12:45,020 --> 00:12:47,420
Producer Song, it seems your effort...

160
00:12:56,580 --> 00:12:58,179
Sorry to let you worry, Lawyer Fang.

161
00:12:58,180 --> 00:12:59,740
That's on me.

162
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,300
I thought about it.

163
00:13:04,660 --> 00:13:06,699
Instead of letting rumors spread,

164
00:13:06,700 --> 00:13:09,100
why don't both of you
clarify it together?

165
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:12,900
We can do a targeted
exclusive interview.

166
00:13:13,060 --> 00:13:14,740
Wanxin, you host it.

167
00:13:15,420 --> 00:13:16,419
Shen Gu will be the guest.

168
00:13:16,420 --> 00:13:19,900
It's bound to draw a huge viewership.

169
00:13:19,980 --> 00:13:21,820
It's a win-win.

170
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:24,379
Unless you have a better idea,
Lawyer Fang.

171
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:25,419
Or

172
00:13:25,420 --> 00:13:28,900
do you want to give this opportunity
to another station?

173
00:13:30,580 --> 00:13:31,779
I think...

174
00:13:31,780 --> 00:13:33,500
Xi, that's a great idea.

175
00:13:38,380 --> 00:13:39,500
Shen Gu,

176
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:40,980
what do you think?

177
00:13:42,380 --> 00:13:45,820
If so, I'll leave Producer Song
and Anchor Xu

178
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,300
to arrange the interview.

179
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:50,540
Deal?

180
00:13:51,700 --> 00:13:52,820
Cheers.

181
00:13:55,660 --> 00:13:57,180
The meat is burnt.

182
00:13:59,180 --> 00:14:01,380
We need to plan
the interview content.

183
00:14:01,610 --> 00:14:04,220
Any requirements, Mr. Shen?

184
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:07,260
I'll follow your lead.

185
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:14,940
It's fine for Mr. Gu
to attend the interview.

186
00:14:15,380 --> 00:14:18,700
Producer Song,

187
00:14:19,380 --> 00:14:20,820
I think you should give me a toast.

188
00:14:22,180 --> 00:14:26,040
I should really give you a toast.

189
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,499
- Right, Lawyer Fang?
- Of course.

190
00:14:27,500 --> 00:14:28,379
I'll fill your glass.

191
00:14:28,380 --> 00:14:29,019
Hey.

192
00:14:29,020 --> 00:14:31,139
- Don't dodge, Lawyer Fang.
- Wait. I can't drink much.

193
00:14:31,140 --> 00:14:31,619
Your tolerance is low?

194
00:14:31,620 --> 00:14:34,979
It's not that. You're mixing drinks.
I don't drink mixed wine.

195
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:35,819
Don't do that.

196
00:14:35,820 --> 00:14:36,940
I can't drink that.

197
00:14:45,960 --> 00:14:47,779
(Gang City Financial News)
Good morning, everyone.

198
00:14:47,780 --> 00:14:49,939
As the Junlin shareholders' meeting
approaches,

199
00:14:49,940 --> 00:14:52,179
Mr. Shen Gu, founder of Qingniao Group,

200
00:14:52,180 --> 00:14:55,580
will soon accept a financial interview
with Ms. Xu Wanxin from our station.

201
00:14:59,340 --> 00:15:01,260
Thank you so much.

202
00:15:09,540 --> 00:15:10,660
What are you smiling about?

203
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:12,860
It feels like a dream.

204
00:15:14,080 --> 00:15:15,660
I never imagined

205
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:19,180
I'd be interviewed by you
as your husband.

206
00:15:23,780 --> 00:15:25,949
We're recording, Mr. Gu.

207
00:15:25,950 --> 00:15:28,660
Have some mercy on us
in the control room.

208
00:15:32,660 --> 00:15:35,059
Save your sweet nothings

209
00:15:35,060 --> 00:15:37,580
for later.

210
00:15:42,100 --> 00:15:43,580
I knew it.

211
00:15:43,660 --> 00:15:45,980
I wouldn't be the only victim.

212
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:48,100
Come on. Say hi...

213
00:15:48,740 --> 00:15:50,780
Don't hang up, Mei.

214
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,580
Who let you in?

215
00:15:54,700 --> 00:15:55,900
I'm his staff.

216
00:15:56,460 --> 00:15:57,580
And?

217
00:15:58,020 --> 00:15:59,460
I'm also his family.

218
00:16:01,780 --> 00:16:04,859
I just came to check in on you,
Producer Song.

219
00:16:04,860 --> 00:16:06,979
Look. Professional team

220
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:08,059
and professional you.

221
00:16:08,060 --> 00:16:09,700
I can also take a quick look around.

222
00:16:14,660 --> 00:16:16,580
I'll get you some coffee when it's over.

223
00:16:22,740 --> 00:16:24,820
Alright. Everyone, get ready.

224
00:16:25,100 --> 00:16:26,100
Three,

225
00:16:26,140 --> 00:16:27,019
two,

226
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:27,819
one.

227
00:16:27,820 --> 00:16:28,539
Start.

228
00:16:28,540 --> 00:16:30,259
(Interview with Mr. Shen Gu,
founder of Qingniao Group)

229
00:16:30,260 --> 00:16:31,939
Good afternoon, everyone.

230
00:16:31,940 --> 00:16:33,259
I'm Xu Wanxin.

231
00:16:33,260 --> 00:16:33,779
Today,

232
00:16:33,780 --> 00:16:37,579
our studio welcomes
a very important guest.

233
00:16:37,580 --> 00:16:40,780
Mr. Shen Gu, founder of Qingniao Group.

234
00:16:41,660 --> 00:16:43,860
Hello, everyone. I'm Shen Gu.

235
00:16:44,060 --> 00:16:45,580
Hello, Mr. Shen.

236
00:16:45,780 --> 00:16:47,059
Thank you

237
00:16:47,060 --> 00:16:49,180
for agreeing to this interview.

238
00:16:49,460 --> 00:16:51,580
It's my honor

239
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:53,460
to be interviewed by you, Miss Xu.

240
00:16:56,100 --> 00:16:57,220
Wanxin,

241
00:16:57,780 --> 00:17:01,460
can you ask Mr. Gu to face the camera?

242
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:48,020
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

243
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:55,100
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

244
00:17:55,820 --> 00:18:01,180
♪You turn and look back at me♪

245
00:18:02,300 --> 00:18:07,820
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

246
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:14,300
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

247
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:21,060
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

248
00:18:22,180 --> 00:18:27,500
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

249
00:18:28,660 --> 00:18:34,460
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

250
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:41,820
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

251
00:18:41,940 --> 00:18:47,620
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

252
00:18:48,300 --> 00:18:54,659
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

253
00:18:54,660 --> 00:18:57,539
♪The promise we made♪

254
00:18:57,540 --> 00:19:01,219
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

255
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:07,819
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

256
00:19:07,820 --> 00:19:14,220
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

257
00:19:14,620 --> 00:19:20,939
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

258
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:26,060
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

259
00:19:26,540 --> 00:19:29,540
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
